g.text: 1. User should be able to view the News Feed with the posts from people they follow.
2. User should be able to page through their feed.
3. User should be able to create posts with Images or Video.
4. User should be able to add a like to a post.
5. User should be able to add a comment to a post.
The system should prioritize availability over consistency since the data is
not critical. Eventual consistency is acceptable in this scenario.
- Posts should become visible within 2 minutes.
- Likes updates should reflect within 2 minutes.
- Comments updates should appear within 2 minutes.
